m. We propose the Gravitino\nSwampland Conjecture, which is consistent with and indeed follows from the KKLT\nand Large Volume scenarios for moduli stabilization in string theory.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 19 Feb 2021 19:00:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 25 Mar 2021 15:40:39 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 24 Aug 2021 13:44:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-20"}
