 both loop\nfeet possibly drive much of the heating, even in the cases where a loop foot\npresents mixed-polarity magnetic flux.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 19 Feb 2021 20:16:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-23"}
